# Auto-detect text files and ensure they are stored as LF in the repo
# On Windows, they will be checked out as CRLF. On Mac/Linux, they stay LF.
* text=auto

# Explicitly declare text files you want to always be normalized
*.js text
*.css text
*.html text

# Declare files that will always be CRLF (e.g., Windows batch files)
*.bat text eol=crlf

# Declare binary files so Git doesn't touch them
*.png binary
*.jpg binary